<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Provisional NOC Letter</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .page {
            background-color: white;
            width: 210mm;
            min-height: 297mm;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .border-frame {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border: 2px dotted #333;
            padding: 4px;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .pattern-border {
            flex-grow: 1;
            border: 1px double #333;
            padding: 40px 50px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Frame lines */
        .page::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 5px;
            left: 5px;
            right: 5px;
            bottom: 5px;
            border: 2px solid #555;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .page::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            bottom: 10px;
            border: 4px double #555;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* Watermark */
        .watermark {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 80%;
            opacity: 0.1;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .watermark img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .content-area {
            font-size: 11pt;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #000;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .logo-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .header-logo {
            height: 80px;
            width: auto;
        }

        .doc-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 12pt;
        }

        .ref-number {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 10pt;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .date-line {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .recipient-block {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .subject {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .salutation {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .bold {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .signature-block {
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .sig-title {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .digital-note {
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        @media (max-width: 850px) {
            .page {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
            }

            .pattern-border {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="page">
        <div class="border-frame">
            <div class="pattern-border">

                <!-- Watermark Background -->
                <div class="watermark">
                    <img src="images/webel.png" alt="Watermark">
                </div>

                <div class="content-area">

                    <!-- Header Logo Image -->
                    <div class="logo-container">
                        <img src="images/webel.png" alt="Webel Logo" class="header-logo">
                    </div>

                    <!-- Document Header -->
                    <div class="doc-title">
                        Provisional NOC of IT/ITeS Renting (Application Number: <%= data?._application_number %>)
                    </div>

                    <div class="ref-number">
                        <%= data?._ref_number %>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Date -->
                    <div class="date-line">
                        Date: <%= data?._current_date %>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Recipient Info -->
                    <div class="recipient-block">
                        Name of Company: <%= data?._company_name %><br>
                            Address: <%= data?._company_address %>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Subject -->
                    <div class="subject">
                        Sub: Permission towards sublet of space of <%= data?._sublet_area_sqft %> sq. ft. super built up
                            area at <%= data?._space_description %>
                    </div>

                    <div class="salutation">
                        Sir,
                    </div>

                    <!-- Body Paragraph 1 -->
                    <p>
                        This has reference to your (self declaration letter with UDIN: <span class="bold">
                            <%= data?._udin %>
                        </span>) regarding the permission for subletting the space to M/S <span class="bold">
                            <%= data?._tenant_name %>
                        </span> at <%= data?._space_description %>.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Body Paragraph 2 -->
                    <p>
                        We would like to confirm our ‘No Objection’ for sub-letting the <%= data?._sublet_area_sqft %>
                            sq. ft. space to M/S <span class="bold">
                                <%= data?._tenant_name %>
                            </span> for carrying out "IT&ITes" activities as declared by M/S <span class="bold">
                                <%= data?._tenant_name %>
                            </span> vide their letter dated <%= data?._tenant_letter_date %>.
                                Your Provisional NOC is effective from <%= data?._noc_start_date %> to <%=
                                        data?._noc_end_date %>.
                                        The NOC would lapse automatically as soon as the said tenancies are expired by
                                        influx of time or the same are determined earlier.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Body Paragraph 3 -->
                    <p>
                        You are advised to comply all legal formalities regarding agreement with your tenants and inform
                        NDITA about the existence of the said firm in Sector-V area.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Body Paragraph 4 -->
                    <p>
                        You will have required to pay permission fees @ Rs.<%= data?._permission_fee_rate %>/- per sq.
                            ft. (permission fees is subject to change from time to time) of the super built up area
                            along with applicable goods & services taxes to W.B.E.I.D.C. Ltd by the 7th day of every
                            calendar month. Such fees shall be paid in advance in every month, irrespective of your
                            receiving rent from the tenant and the non-payment of Permission fees or any kind of
                            non-compliance may cause automatic cancellation/withdrawal of the NOC granted.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Body Paragraph 5 -->
                    <p>
                        Moreover, you are requested to inform us about the vacancy and fill up of premises within the
                        month of its happening otherwise permission fees will be charged upto date as mentioned in the
                        agreement without any reversal thereon.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Closing -->
                    <p>
                        Thanking you,
                    </p>

                    <!-- Signature Block -->
                    <div class="signature-block">
                        <div class="sig-title">Authorised Signatory</div>
                        <div class="sig-title">For Managing Director, Webel</div>
                        <div class="digital-note">(This document is digitally signed and does not require physical
                            signature)</div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>